items.headline: All that every professional needs to know about Cyber Law.
objectives_summary: In this course, the professionals will get to learn about why Cyberlaw is important to them, independent of whatever profession they are practicing and working and what they as working professionals need to know about Cyberlaw in order to be feeling more empowered while dealing with cyberspace related activities.   Unlike other disciplines, Cyberlaw is an all encompassing discipline which impacts every professional who is using computers, computer systems, computer networks, computer resources and communication devices and also data and information in the electronic form.  Cyberlaw is impacting all professionals. This course will enable professionals of all categories who have familiarity with basic principles of Cyberlaw which impact their day-to-day professional activities and how they can take appropriate caution and care to be on the right side of Cyberlaw as they go forward in the direction of performing their professional duties.
